@startuml
autonumber
actor Organizer
participant "Browser" as Client
participant "Event Controller" as Controller
participant "Dinner Event Service" as Service
participant "Event Repository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Organizer -> Client: Compila form creazione evento
Client -> Controller: POST /events/create
Controller -> Service: createDinnerEvent(eventDTO, user)
Service -> Service: Valida dati evento
Service -> Repo: save(event)
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO dinner_events ...
DB --> Repo: Event ID
Repo --> Service: Saved Event
Service --> Controller: Event ID
Controller --> Client: Redirect /events/{id}
Client -> Organizer: Mostra Dettagli Evento
@enduml
